  "detailed_description": "<h1>Featured DLC</h1><p>Bonus content includes the Original Soundtrack and Memorial Book.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>    The bonus contents will be placed in your Steam folder:<br>    ..\\Steam\\SteamApps\\common\\BlazBlue Centralfiction\\Digital Extras[/list]<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/586140/extras/22f1ec61af13f5eac725017154c2e748.avif?t=1653281343\" width=358 height=230 /></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Re-live Arc System Works' trademark beautiful visuals and deep expressive combat, with improved netplay! Now is the perfect time for veterans and new challengers alike to return to the Azure! Choose from 35 unique anime-inspired characters utilizing various new and refined system mechanics. The Wheel of Fate turns again!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/586140/extras/16f3b8508c30d78abbace256f194ea01.poster.avif?t=1653281343\" width=398 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/586140/extras/16f3b8508c30d78abbace256f194ea01.webm?t=1653281343\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/586140/extras/16f3b8508c30d78abbace256f194ea01.mp4?t=1653281343\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>A high-speed 2D fighting game combined with a breathtaking visual novel, the bookend to this chapter of the series breathes in new life...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/586140/extras/1b09d014fa78373a452839f3b0cf2de6.poster.avif?t=1653281343\" width=398 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/586140/extras/1b09d014fa78373a452839f3b0cf2de6.webm?t=1653281343\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/586140/extras/1b09d014fa78373a452839f3b0cf2de6.mp4?t=1653281343\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul>",
